{"tid":2013371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：立法會選舉日為9月6日 進入票站需量度體溫 有發燒症狀需要在特別投票間進行投票","createTime":"2020-05-12T09:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T11:29:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f92dc8ea2a24dbc48b453fb80ca43ac8b91750","tid":2013371,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"政府今日（12日）向立法會提交文件，透露今屆立法會選舉日為9月6日，提名期則由7月中旬至下旬，確實日期將於稍後憲報公佈。今次選舉料設610個投票站，投票時間為上午7時30分至晚上10時30分。文件亦提及，因應疫情持續政府將在投票站採取多項防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n今次選舉將設610個投票站，選舉事務處稱，已初步聯絡400多個非政府場地的管理單位，徵求他們同意借場地，以去年區議會選舉中曾用作投票站的場地為主。而因應武漢肺炎疫情持續，文件亦提到為防止病毒在票站散播，將採取多項安全措施，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投票站工作人員必須戴上口罩及手套，在投票站入口鋪設已經噴灑漂白水的地墊，選民、候選人及代理人進入票站時須量度體溫，有發燒症狀的選民會被引領到較為隱蔽的特別投票間投票等</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200512/I3CLJZ3FC2DAEUBSR3AAQZAMPA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200512%2FI3CLJZ3FC2DAEUBSR3AAQZAMPA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=06e016af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200512%2FI3CLJZ3FC2DAEUBSR3AAQZAMPA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=5c043587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200512/I3CLJZ3FC2DAEUBSR3AAQZAMPA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"644fbe316fa16fba75e1a17db94bd083d3985f2a","tid":2013371,"uid":126731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,